I wonder why everybody want's to use XSLT on the client side. On te Server side it is so powerful and works like a charme with PHP:
// XML
$xml_doc = new DOMDocument();
$xml_doc->load("file1.xml");// XSL
$xsl_doc = new DOMDocument();
$xsl_doc->load("file.xsl");// Proc
$proc = new XSLTProcessor();
$proc->importStylesheet($xsl_doc);
$newdom = $proc->transformToDoc($xml_doc);// Output 
print $newdom->saveXML();
